Hadi! Hadi!

00:16:19.850 --> 00:16:21.310
Kuririn-san!

00:16:21.520 --> 00:16:23.850
Geldi!

00:16:24.060 --> 00:16:26.650
Kuririn-san, bunu buldum!

00:16:26.860 --> 00:16:28.980
