00:16:53.840 --> 00:16:56.970
Kuririn, Gohan-kun, hadi artık gidelim.

00:16:57.180 --> 00:16:58.850
Doğru. Evet.

00:17:19.870 --> 00:17:21.580
Burası göl.

00:17:21.790 --> 00:17:24.000
